---
import Layout from "../layouts/Default.astro";
import Prose from "../components/Prose.astro";
---
<Layout title={'About'} description={'About Matt Brailsford, Technical Team Lead at Umbraco Commerce, co-founder of CODECABIN, and creator of the UMB.FYI newsletter.'}>
    <article class="w-full py-7 md:py-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl leading-none text-black uppercase mb-2 md:text-6xl">About</h1>
        <Prose>
            <p>I’m a Staff Engineer at Umbraco HQ, where I’m building <a href="https://github.com/umbraco/Umbraco.AI">Umbraco AI</a> — a provider-agnostic AI platform that brings intelligent features into the CMS backoffice. Think semantic search, conversational agents, prompt management, and more — all with a flexible architecture that lets you plug in OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Amazon, or Microsoft AI Foundry.</p>
            <p>Before that, I spent years deep in the Umbraco Commerce codebase, leading the e-commerce side of the platform.</p>
            <p>Beyond the day job, I’m the co-founder of <a href="https://codecab.in">CODECABIN</a>, an intimate developer retreat for the Umbraco community, and the creator of <a href="https://umb.fyi">UMB.FYI</a>, a newsletter rounding up the latest from the Umbraco ecosystem.</p>
            <p>I’m passionate about open-source, developer experience, and building tools that get out of your way. If any of that resonates, say hello.</p>
        </Prose>
    </article>
</Layout>